{"tid":1031534,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果當初我肯更加坦誠相對，會唔會有唔同結局","createTime":"2019-02-21T16:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T05:40:39.000Z","uid":46457,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50207fe8b206e6ecefbebe7db845b965c47d91aa","tid":1031534,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:50:44.000Z","msg":"分左手好耐都仲諗緊<br />\n<br />\n如果我當時肯去改，更加坦白自己唔去埋怨太多做更多主動，對方會唔會愛我多d<br />\n<br />\n點解一直唔肯公開，係咪嫌我唔夠出色，唔見得人，定係朋友係第一，其實唔太鐘意我揾我攝時間 ... 多疑同無安全感係魔鬼，如果一段關係當中包含咁多不確定性，係咪代表根本大家唔適合，對對方冇信心，拍左咁耐都唔了解對方諗乜<br />\n<br />\n但單方面努力又有乜用，雙方都唔肯溝通，唔肯坦率d根本好難走落去，日日估佢仲愛唔愛自己真係好攰 ... 仲要完左都每我好介意呢堆冇答案既問題"},{"pid":"db4c2420fbf1f213a56bfda03785c552f06d5869","tid":1031534,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"656d1108f591b55babbab9a568f3861a12256f51","tid":1031534,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"1fecea5845ee8461b9eaf70aee44679b7184fc63","tid":1031534,"uid":238367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔會⋯<br />\n<br />\n你只會發現你付出左好大 但得到既回報係好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfb960b2e50ba0981cd02fe1e28e4deec8708dd","tid":1031534,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db4c2420fbf1f213a56bfda03785c552f06d5869","tid":1031534,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"唔會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"竟然有幸見到浮雲哥"},{"pid":"3e1463d0a75dd85aee4be5b78f054176747cdf87","tid":1031534,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fecea5845ee8461b9eaf70aee44679b7184fc63","tid":1031534,"uid":238367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔會⋯<br />\n<br />\n你只會發現你付出左好大 但得到既回報係好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"